The paper deals with transmitter optimization for a MISO broadcast channel subject to linear constraints, which is a problem in information theory (cs.IT). The application of the proposed method is in a multicell scenario with partial cell cooperation, which involves networked systems (cs.NI) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also evaluates the effectiveness of the proposed method in a system scenario, which involves machine learning (cs.MM) and learning theory (cs.LG).
